The '''North Borneo Frodo Society''' was the [[Tolkien Societies|Tolkien society]] in Malaysia, founded by Mr. McKee in 1971. [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] himself was a member of this society, and his membership card was reproduced in ''[[The Tolkien Family Album]]''.<ref>{{HM|Album}}, p. 85</ref>
